00:50:53.200 --> 00:50:55.940
So there was an idea
conceived in one dimension

00:50:55.940 --> 00:51:00.180
for a simple atom structure,
and this idea worked even better

00:51:00.180 --> 00:51:02.250
for real atoms and
in three dimensions.

