00:52:20.530 --> 00:52:23.190
increases your
phase space density

00:52:23.190 --> 00:52:26.250
by 15 orders of magnitude.

00:52:26.250 --> 00:52:32.720
So this is why molasses and
the MOT were a real milestone.

00:52:32.720 --> 00:52:35.570
Now, with 15 orders
of magnitude,

00:52:35.570 --> 00:52:38.400
you are just 4 or 5
orders of magnitude

00:52:38.400 --> 00:52:41.520
from Bose-Einstein
condensation, and we

00:52:41.520 --> 00:52:44.400
