01:19:53.190 --> 01:19:58.940
and say the time derivative
of the rate equation

01:19:58.940 --> 01:20:03.380
has to relax to
the steady state.

01:20:03.380 --> 01:20:07.410
This is nothing else than
rewriting the equation above.

01:20:07.410 --> 01:20:12.480
But by rewriting the
