01:20:12.480 --> 01:20:17.210
we find now the
prefactor in front of-- I

01:20:17.210 --> 01:20:20.470
mean, here, what you have is
the time derivative is given

01:20:20.470 --> 01:20:22.440
by the difference
from steady state.

01:20:22.440 --> 01:20:24.630
And this is the
relaxation coefficient.

01:20:24.630 --> 01:20:28.100
And the relaxation coefficient
is-- that's the solution.

01:20:28.100 --> 01:20:31.240
You just have to do the
