01:20:38.960 --> 01:20:42.230
One is going from the
upper to the lower

01:20:42.230 --> 01:20:44.260
and from the lower
to the upper state.

01:20:44.260 --> 01:20:46.330
And each of those rates
has been expressed

01:20:46.330 --> 01:20:47.860
